ON Windows 
just go to wwww.python.orgs/downloads/

select and download the version you want to install!

Click next pretty much everytime let the settings be default if you're a new user!

Check the "Add Python to PATH" button.

After installation to check :
Goto to cmd (start menu search- cmd)
type - python
>>>
there it should take to python environment and its verison with few details would be shown.
